{"tid":1401512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母冷氣軍師 送頭送頭送你老母","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T15:51:52.000Z","uid":29132,"like":17,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5f1f7c7c71902ef4e18a58a28936bf07985b1d73","tid":1401512,"uid":29132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:51:46.000Z","msg":"成撚日話人送頭，人地諗咩你知唔知呀，只係識坐係冷氣到指指點點。<span style=\"color: red;\">成日話留力留力，唔係最後一戰，我屌你老母呀，冷氣軍師就只係識屋企指指點點，從來唔會走上前線，即係咩？</span><span style=\"color: red;\">前線已經唔會再有援兵</span>，佢地只有個班手足會齊上齊落，對一班冇援兵嘅人嚟講，佢地永遠都係最後一戰，冇一個手足就真係冇一個手足，咁叫唔到全部人都有，與其一齊面對。<br />\n<br />\n人地願意付出所有而戰，而你地班人有冇回應過人地嘅努力呀？屌你老母，你地班撚樣連面對警察嘅勇氣都冇呀，屌你老母！<br />\n<br />\n隨便負評"},{"pid":"3ea0c9637c4808fa357065d7f3796fb37a58884c","tid":1401512,"uid":158889,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:52:10.000Z","msg":"5毛出哂手明顯先係鬼 成班冷氣軍師連網上戰線都打唔好就指指點點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849799010c192f4f848692250e70f87c7d8b3136","tid":1401512,"uid":29132,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:52:12.000Z","msg":"屌你老母冷氣軍師"},{"pid":"2643373a663713d880db4cdd3a3de939383e2cf5","tid":1401512,"uid":29132,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:52:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母冷氣軍師"},{"pid":"960ec2f43f1ea3ed3932c23038c021ead60a94bf","tid":1401512,"uid":29132,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:52:43.000Z","msg":"負評我啦屌你"},{"pid":"b0f9ceb78c39f6b4f15b3e926ea885cbb380f264","tid":1401512,"uid":29132,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:52:55.000Z","msg":"屌你老母冷氣軍師"},{"pid":"715a80b64933d12ca6eac853641cb2d10f33c4de","tid":1401512,"uid":29132,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:53:05.000Z","msg":"口講就叻"},{"pid":"54c75f150f924aa8f781e388fee66be20e21d565","tid":1401512,"uid":29132,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:53:37.000Z","msg":"落